            <abstract>
                <p>Miracle of <persName ref="PRS4377Gabriel"/> concerning the construction of a church dedicated to the Saint
                    in the country of Neqlon/Niqlon. According to the edition of 
                    <bibl><ptr target="bm:Makweriya1976DersanaGabriel"/><citedRange unit="page">146–149</citedRange></bibl>,
                    it forms part of the monthly reading for the 19th of Miyāzyā in the <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7815DersanaGa"/>.
                    It is similar to and possibly another version of <ref type="work" corresp="LIT7811GenbMir"/>. A relation to or possibly even
                    identity with <ref type="work" corresp="LIT5901DersanaGabrielNaglon"/> cannot be excluded, either.</p>
            </abstract>
